<item>
            <title>[SEC-243] SessionRegistryImpl.getAllSessions(Object) incorrectly includes expired and destroyed sessions</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-243</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The function SessionRegistryImpl.getAllSessions(principal) returns all session associated with the principal, even it is marked as expired. This is in violation of the SessionRegistry interface contract.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix is to filter out any expired session information return by function sessionRegistry.getAllSessions(principal)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13687">SEC-243</key>
            <summary>SessionRegistryImpl.getAllSessions(Object) incorrectly includes expired and destroyed sessions</summary>
